lo hunting strategy, and a new article to be published soon)which have been published on the stratics website. While I may not be a master magician, I am not a newbie to the game and have put some thought into how to play it.  I'm interested in, and respect your opinions, I would ask that you give the same respect to myself and others that post on these boards.<br><br>Cetus<br>The Nameless<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
